{"title_page": "Realtors Association of Edmonton", "text_new": "{{Orphan|date=May 2015}}\n\nWith roots dating to 1909, the REALTORS\u00ae Association of Edmonton (RAE) is a professional services association of more than 3,500 professionals serving the Greater Edmonton area. Governed by a volunteer board of directors, the association\u2019s membership includes REALTORS\u00ae and brokers alike. The association plays an active role in professionally developing its members and in enhancing the reputation of REALTORS\u00ae in the community.<ref>{{cite web|title=About the Realtors Association of Edmonton|url=https://realtorsofedmonton.com/web/RAE_Public/About_the_Association/RAE_Public/About_the_Association/About_the_Association_New.aspx|website=Realtors Association of Edmonton|publisher=Realtors Association of Edmonton|accessdate=May 6, 2015}}</ref>\n\n==History==\n* 1909 - Edmonton Real Estate Exchange Created\n* 1927 - Edmonton Real Estate Association Created\n* 1952 - Evolved into the Edmonton Real Estate Board cooperative Listing Bureau Ltd.\n* 2007 - Name change to REALTORS\u00ae Association of Edmonton\n\n==See also==\n* [[Canadian Real Estate Association]]\n* [[Alberta Real Estate Association]]\n* [[Real Estate Council of Alberta]]\n\n==External links==\n* [https://realtorsofedmonton.com REALTORS\u00ae Association of Edmonton]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{real estate-ca}}\n\n[[Category:Real estate industry trade groups]]\n[[Category:Real estate in Canada]]\n", "text_old": "{{Orphan|date=May 2015}}\n\nWith roots dating to 1909, the REALTORS\u00ae Association of Edmonton (RAE) is a professional services association of more than 3,500 professionals serving the Greater Edmonton area. Governed by a volunteer board of directors, the association\u2019s membership includes REALTORS\u00ae and brokers alike. The association plays an active role in professionally developing its members and in enhancing the reputation of REALTORS\u00ae in the community.<ref>{{cite web|title=About the Realtors Association of Edmonton|url=https://realtorsofedmonton.com/web/RAE_Public/About_the_Association/RAE_Public/About_the_Association/About_the_Association_New.aspx|website=Realtors Association of Edmonton|publisher=Realtors Association of Edmonton|accessdate=May 6, 2015}}</ref>\n\n==History==\n* 1909 - Edmonton Real Estate Exchange Created\n* 1927 - Edmonton Real Estate Association Created\n* 1952 - Evolved into the Edmonton Real Estate Board cooperative Listing Bureau Ltd.\n* 2007 - Name change to REALTORS\u00ae Association of Edmonton\n\n==See also==\n* [[Canadian Real Estate Association]]\n* [[Alberta Real Estate Association]]\n* [[Real Estate Council of Alberta]]\n* [[Toronto Real Estate Board]]\n\n==External links==\n* [https://realtorsofedmonton.com REALTORS\u00ae Association of Edmonton]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{real estate-ca}}\n\n[[Category:Real estate industry trade groups]]\n[[Category:Real estate in Canada]]\n", "name_user": "Yunshui", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removing link(s):Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Toronto Real Estate Boardclosed as delete (XFDcloser)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Realtors_Association_of_Edmonton"}
